CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 26, 1966, pg. 12B reads: "Preparing HIll's "Health-O-Rama" - Key community leaders, representing the Steering Committee for the United Fund's "Health-O-Rama," get instructions for the need for volunteers. The program will be held at the Savoy Ballroom, April 14 through 19."
TitMainTitle: Community leader representatives of the Health-O-Rama Steering Committee, including Monsignor Paul Bassompierre, gathered for meeting in interior, another version
